# LexCura Logo Setup

## Logo File Required

Create a folder `assets/` in your project root and add your LexCura logo as:
`assets/lexcura_logo.png`

**Logo specifications:**
- Format: PNG with transparent background
- Size: 200x60px (or similar aspect ratio)  
- Style: Should work on dark backgrounds
- Colors: Gold/white preferred to match dashboard theme

## If you don't have a logo yet:

1. **Quick solution**: Create a simple text logo using any graphics tool
2. **Text alternative**: The dashboard will show "LexCura" text if image fails to load
3. **Professional option**: Use Canva or similar to create a branded logo

## File structure:
```
lexcura-dashboard/
├── app.py
├── assets/
│   └── lexcura_logo.png  (your logo here)
├── requirements.txt
└── ...
```
